title: Patch 7.19 Oceania
body: Is Oceania supposed to get the features of patch 7.19 that the rest of the world has? I don't know if it's just my client, but I have not received Evelynn rework or the new runes. SO, is this a problem-or is this just normal and are you going to release it in another patch? Please answer!

replies.body:
Hey summoner, 

New runes aren't out on any server until preseason (patch will come out on November 8th for that). 
Evelynn was only recently released on PBE so it will be a while before she comes out on live servers for any region.
